data.title: What are some comedies that you think are great films, but weren't well received?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 3): One of my favorite comedies is a movie called, “Cheaper to keep her”. It is one of the most “politically incorrect” movies ever and is a riot. The critics treatment of it is rather savage. Just goes to show how humorless the PC crowd is.
